@startuml seq_weekly_schedule
!theme plain
title Sequence Diagram: Fetch Weekly Matrix Schedule (Aggregator)

skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "HR User" as User
participant "React SPA" as Client
participant "Kong API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Leave Service" as Leave
database "PostgreSQL (HA)" as PG

User -> Client : Navigate to "Weekly Schedule"
Client -> Gateway : GET /api/leaves/schedule/weekly
Gateway -> Leave : Route Request

Leave -> Leave : Verify JWT Token & RBAC

Note over Leave, PG: Complex Aggregation Flow
Leave -> PG : 1. Query Target Users (Based on Role/Dept)
Leave -> PG : 2. Generate 7-Days Date Array (generate_series)
Leave -> PG : 3. Query APPROVED Leaves for Target Users (7 Days)
Leave -> PG : 4. Query Attendance Logs for Target Users (7 Days)
Leave -> PG : 5. Query System Settings (Holidays)

Leave -> Leave : Map Data: User x 7 Days Matrix
Leave -> Leave : Apply Status Logic (WORKING, LEAVE, HOLIDAY, UNEXCUSED)
Leave -> Leave : Compute Late/Early Status from Logs

Leave -> Client : Return Aggregated JSON Matrix
Client -> User : Render Weekly Grid UI
@enduml